data.description: $0 down with qualified credit* Also receive an additional 1% credit towards closing cost when using our preferred lender ( Rose Flores NMLS# 2246096 Legacy Mutual Mortgage.)     Stunning 5-Bedroom Home in Far West San Antonio with Primary Bedroom Downstairs! This modern gem, built in 2017, sits on a spacious corner lot and boasts an impressive open-concept design. Enjoy two spacious living areas and a beautifully equipped kitchen with ample granite counter space. The primary bedroom on the main floor offers convenience and privacy. Step outside to the inviting screened-in patio, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. This is a dream family home in a great location.
